<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿlmny ạ̉rwḥ mṭrḥ mạ trwḥ .. ḥbyb ạlrwḥ wạ̉gẖnylk
 ạ̉ḥly̱ ạlklmạt wyạ ạlngẖmạt .. wbkl tẖbạt ạ̉ṣly lk)2
 (wạ̉nạ wạtẖq fyk wmslm lyk .. wʿyny ʿlyk lmạ ạ̉jy lk)2
 ạlqrạr- (dạ ạ̹nt ạ̹lhy ạlly mkfyny .. wmạly synyny bkl ạlkẖyr
 dạ ạ̉nạ kẖdạmk ạ̉ʿysẖ qdạmk .. dạ ạ̉nạ fy klạmk qlby ạ̉syr)2
 dạ ạ̉nạ fy klạmk qlby ạ̉syr
 2- (ʿlmny ạ̉ʿysẖ mạyhmnysẖ .. gẖyr ạ̹ny ạ̉ʿysẖ ʿmry fy rḍạk
 wạfḍl gẖryb sẖạyl ạlṣlyb .. wbsẖkr ạ̉syb ạlkl mʿạk)2
 (jwh ạlạ̉twn tḥfẓ wtṣwn .. mạ ạ̹nt ạlḥnwn wạ̉nạ fy ḥmạk)2
 3- (bạḥbk yswʿ wbkl kẖsẖwʿ .. wsṭ ạldmwʿ ạ̉rnm lk
 ṭwl ạlṭryq fy rḥb wḍyq .. tbqy̱ ạlṣdyq wạ̉slm lk)2
 (wyzyd ạ̹ymạny wạ̉ʿysẖ zmạny .. bsẖkl tạny qryb mnk)2</lyrics>
